bdremote-ng 0.5
---------------

Adds support for printing the battery charge %.

022 Battery information.
023 Merge patch from Paul Bender: release support.
024 Merge patch from Paul Bender: namespace support 
025 Add missing variable.

bdremote-ng 0.4
---------------

Adds support for repeating a key (after an initial delay), when
its being held down. A number of more or less serious bugs were
fixed in this release. Also adds doxygen comments.

002 Implement support for repeat.
008 Add doxygen comments for all interfaces.
015 Running in background results in no remote control.
017 Add doxygen for all files.
018 High cpu usage.
019 Repeat is erratic.
020 Typos.
021 Not working when another HID is also to be used.

